                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18251208-99-off495 t18251208-99-crimeloc498"></join>. Two of these pots are mine; I have seen the prisoner about the neighbourhood - he used to work at a livery stable opposite to me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18251208-99-person562">
                  HENRY 
                  BELL
               <interp inst="t18251208-99-person562" type="surname" value="BELL"></interp>
